room_title: Escape room "The Psychic" by Challenge Escape Rooms in New York
room_description: Your friends insisted that you come along to get a psychic reading. Once you enter the psychic's room, the door suddenly closes behind you, locking you all in! You are filled with dread as it's clear your lives are in danger... Can you use what's in the psychic's room to find a way out before she traps you for all of eternity?
